h3. Problem Definition
The Help Center is not accessible if a user is not yet logged in. All the user can see is the login page when accessing {{https://mydomain.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portals}}
On https://support.atlassian.com , there is a customised version where the Help Center is accessible without logging in: https://support.atlassian.com/customer/servicedesk-portal

